In[48]:
nrows = 6
ncols = 4
count = 0
position = 0

for i in range(nrows):
    check = 0
    for j in range(ncols):
        plt.subplot(nrows , ncols , position+1)
        plt.imshow(imgs[count+1])
        if check == 1:
            plt.imshow(cv2.cvtColor(imgs[count + 1],cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY), cmap='gray')
        if check == 2:
            plt.imshow(cv2.cvtColor(imgs[count + 1], cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
        if check == 3:
            plt.imshow(cv2.cvtColor(imgs[count + 1], cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY), cmap = 'pink')
        position = position + 1
        check = check + 1
    count = count + 1
    if count == 3 : 
        count = 0
